data.description: Step into this incredibly charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom ranch in the heart of Miami Township. The open living room and lofty ceilings make the nearly 1500 sq feet feel even more spacious and inviting. Upon opening the front door, you are immediately bathed in natural light. Through the arched doorway, the kitchen greets you with a delightful wall of windows and glass-front cabinets, perfect for displaying your personal style. The pass-through window seamlessly connects the main areas of the home. Adding character and functionality, the built-in corner cabinet perfectly compliments the  dining room with plenty of space for hosting dinner guests. Flowing right into the living room, the updated flooring directs you into the heart of the home, featuring a cozy fireplace next to the back door which leads to your own private, backyard oasis. Complete with a shed for storage and a paver patio, the backyard is perfect for enjoying time outside. Stepping back through the appealing patio doors, you will find the two guest bedrooms are carpeted, adding a touch of relaxation. The spacious primary bedroom overlooks the well-maintained backyard, providing a serene view through a sizable window, displaying ample natural light. The primary bathroom is equipped with a double vanity, roomy closet, and a relaxing tub, all under an alluring skylight, inviting you to unwind after a long day. Don't miss the opportunity to make this unique and charming house your home.
